snippet.title: Puffmin Quest Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
Puffmin Quest is a Pikmin 2 hack made by Captain Salty. Explore the Shroom Isles and beyond with Captain Salty and Co-pilot Pepper as they try and track down someone who went missing on PNF-404. What secrets and discoveries will you find in this all new world?

Join the discord: https://discord.gg/KrsNtT6fhn
Twitter: https://twitter.com/PuffHacker

Music made by Teddiursayoshi and Kyng 

#pikmin #pikmin2 #pikmin4
